    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The crowd since most of them were international, helping me to relate with them.",
          "name": "Don John Sam",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "One of the things I like about SCAC is the number of events organized and the support of the teachers to organize the same",
          "name": "Piyush Mhaskar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Secondly, the diversity of this college, every year majority of the students are from different states and also different countries.  So you get to connect with them",
          "name": "Piyush Mhaskar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The cafeteria is very good and there is also sitting facilities",
          "name": "Himesh Rathi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The first thing I liked about the college is the teaching staffs are very much well trained and their teaching style is also very good and as a student I understand everything as the teacher teaches.",
          "name": "Ritik Agarwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The second thing a liked about the college is that the college is not so much exam oriented rather it focuses more on practicals and assignments. Their are external papers aswell but it focuses more on internals and assignments and group activities.",
          "name": "Ritik Agarwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college is also located in Pune. Pune is the startup hub of many new enterprises and many MNC’s are also located in Pune. Hence, the location of the college is also very nice.",
          "name": "Ritik Agarwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The opportunity you get after getting in this college is amazing. Most student of my batch are coming from different cites all over the India.",
          "name": "Abhishek Umbare",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college have a tons of club through which you can learn new skills and increase ur confidence",
          "name": "Abhishek Umbare",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college even interact with students from other campuses of symbiosis through student exchange program. From countries like France and Japan",
          "name": "Abhishek Umbare",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College provides placements to very few students",
          "name": "Ashi Chakradhar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "there are mixed reviews about placement ,with some students reporting lower placement rate or pac than expected",
          "name": "Shubhankar Deb",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Location: Remote location, limited access to public transport.",
          "name": "Krutika Deepak Adhav",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Also i think that the college should give the permission to use the lift of the college by everyone",
          "name": "Sahil Ansari",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "There’s no infrastructure in the college just a ramp and canteen that’s it no place to hang out or play sports students can’t use the lift as well we have to walk down 4 floor up and down for so many times we are sick or changing classes all the time",
          "name": "Rashi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers change the lecture times according to there convince and there’s no completion of syllabus on time students are always late there no dicielin in the college every projects are no attendance is providing for participation in the college clubs",
          "name": "Rashi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "No ground and garden in the college and nothing to do besides engaging in clubs.",
          "name": "Krish lakhotia",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Number of security guards to be increased",
          "name": "Shubham Verma",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The faculty takes a bit of time to complete any process",
          "name": "Shruti Shitole",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college has a lot of big events and gigs. But the events are not that great as compared to other colleges in Pune. MIT-WPU offers much better events and celebraties also visit their college.",
          "name": "Ritik Agarwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
